pen to discoveries about the Bible that seem nontraditional or even antireligious.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aRabbinical literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aRevelation on Sinai. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / History.2bisacsh1 aCollins, John, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300158953?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300158953423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300158953/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles